cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image processing and analysis for the lane-keeping system.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also likely as the paper focuses on the security and safety of the lane-keeping system under physical world adversarial attacks.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves deep learning-based LKASes.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper involves the use of AI techniques for attacking the LKAS.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the control system of the LKAS and its vulnerability to attacks.
